Seahorse Mesos docker image
===========================

The image contains Mesos, Spark and python libraries required for running SX inside a docker container.

1. Build the image

   $ docker build -t docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/deepsense_io/deepsense-mesos-spark:2.0.0 .

2. Running the image (substitute {MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER} with proper IP address)

   $ docker run --net=host -it docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/deepsense_io/deepsense-mesos-spark:2.0.0 /bin/bash
   $ docker run --env LIBPROCESS_ADVERTISE_IP={MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER} --env LIBPROCESS_IP={MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER} --net=host -it docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/deepsense_io/deepsense-mesos-spark:2.0.0 /bin/bash

3. Running spark-shell on mesos://10.10.1.221:5050 cluster (substitute {MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER} with proper IP address)

   $ LIBPROCESS_ADVERTISE_IP={MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER}
   $ LIBPROCESS_IP={MACHINE_IP_VISIBLE_FROM_CLUSTER}
   $ spark-shell --master mesos://10.10.1.221:5050 --conf spark.executor.uri=http://d3kbcqa49mib13.cloudfront.net/spark-2.0.0-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz

4. Publishing the image

   $ docker push docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/deepsense_io/deepsense-mesos-spark:2.0.0
